node.text:
“Love Leopard! A timeless classic that matches everything and works for every occasion. It's also such a perfect print for kids - camouflage spots of all sorts, an iconic in our Mini Rodini Basic collection” Cassandra Rhodin, Founder and Creative Director @cassandra_rhodin

Shop our organic Basic at minirodini.com 
Link in bio! 

#cassandrarhodin #minirodini #basics #kidswear #leopardprint

node.text:
Last but not least on the school list: the backpack!!    
And just like all our backpacks, our new Bow and Walrus bags are made from 100% ♻️ polyester. 

#minirodini #backtoschool #recycledpolyester #backpack
